Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到  会以这种形式相见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是豚鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园都市就是实验动物的饲养场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些小鬼都是家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是眼下  掌握著拯救菲布莉的关键的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵  好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验动物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是泰瑞丝缇娜·木原·莱夫雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦野也下来游嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要是面子问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被别人利用了还忍气吞声的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这个圈子  被小瞧了就没有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.88,small,NTP,0,0,0,,你不游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.84,small,NTP,0,0,0,,我乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被假消息牵著鼻子走  还不都是你的责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭什么要我们来给你擦屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是不给报酬  就不要发牢骚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不也说过被弄得团团转还一肚子火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞一场大龙凤也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  麦野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧…虽然没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去活动活动筋骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副嘴脸变得不错了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没少经历这座城市的黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对深深的黑暗感到绝望和胆怯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后呢  有否因此而诅咒这座学院都市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后发现我所说的话是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园都市是实验场地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生全都是豚鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  想问我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是想让我摸摸头给予你安慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救我一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她名字叫菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个人造的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不做的话她只剩下72小时的命了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道菲布莉是暗部的人制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你应该知道点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多克隆体被杀害还真有脸说出这种天真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的那个什么小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在这座城市的黑暗中诞生的一只豚鼠罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里活下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么被黑暗吞噬成为家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么将黑暗打破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此以外没有任何办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实窥探过你所说的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了相当的震撼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也自暴自弃过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我从里面救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是在这座城市里邂逅的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有许多对我十分重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这座城市的话  我是不会遇到他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也有不少让人生气的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要讨厌这座学院城市我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁制造了菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目的是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是骗你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要告诉你真相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的话  你又能相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我决定相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没放哦  巧克力糖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是相信我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了相信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我关于菲布莉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有什么要告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你告诉我  否则我就不走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵  快给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  告诉我关于菲布莉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯米卡莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人应该这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯米卡莱特  指的是菲布莉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时应该只有理论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说那几个小少年成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人就是制造了菲布莉的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要突显一下自己的存在感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突显…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个活动快要开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学究会?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓突显存在感指的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了那么一点事让菲布莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么一点?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.96,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(565,646)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有被选中的超能力者大人才能说出的大话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  你给我好好记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座学园都市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.97,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(563,645)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要将超能力者这个名片发出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算像你这样的实验动物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会有许多好朋友向你靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连实验动物都当不了的那些人的黑暗是有多深不可测
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不要吓得尿裤子哦  臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  你去找那位泰瑞丝缇娜小姐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事出突然  因此没和大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个凯米卡莱特就是菲布莉的正式称呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人想要在学究会搞什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方并没有说得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要是婚后她们看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个谈到菲布莉的人也去了学究会会场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上最近将会举办的活动  我猜应该就那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是医院的那位医生介绍你去见泰瑞丝缇娜小姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样子长得像一个可爱的吉祥物  到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位医生还说过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说现有的糖能支撑菲布莉生命的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约72小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,72小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我筛选一下学究会的参加者试试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举办方以及参加的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉  醒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  午安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天带了一些好东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道发现什么线索了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸…不是…关于那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几乎一直都在找那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是还没有任何发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不过  我们一定能找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天来是有关别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想给菲布莉妹妹一份礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们看到了一件挺可爱的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该会很衬菲布莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们说这是送给菲布莉的礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那打开看看咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给菲布莉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子  湾内  泡浮谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必言谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是见证友谊的小礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是菲布莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸好红  难道是发烧了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋晕晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃糖吧  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻不容缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在学究会会场看到的就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  湾内  泡浮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这照片是?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去年学究会的参加者名单里的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有富春树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在前年的学究会获得了最优秀奖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且几乎每年都是名列前茅的获奖者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长年在学究会名列前茅的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学园都市也是屈指可数的才子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他啊  完全不认识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  果然和高等级能力者相比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才子就显得毫不起眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连实验动物都当不了的家伙们的黑暗是有多深不可测
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这个人今年好像没参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄泉川老师也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「往年的获奖参加者今年都没怎么来」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独今年  有好多人都没参加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  这当中可能有他的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有相关数据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只剩下第一实验室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  看不见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉  不热了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食欲也恢复了  姑且可以松口气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春  你一直在调查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得闲不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫有富的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前好像自主退学了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧  他都聪明到能拿奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这么有才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是用在正道上该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会想要掳走菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会又是什么黑暗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然还是头一次知道学究会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过一想到有人就算没有能力也在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中还是略感欣慰的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  黄泉川老师  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来目前的情况还是因为证据不足而无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这也是意料之中的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然遭到了施压
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.99,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(563,645)}<Antiskill>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就明白警备员是无法依靠的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人?  你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在想泰瑞丝缇娜说的那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.00,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(747.2,641.6)}<Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一说常盘台的超电磁砲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的人应该不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不少人是因此而认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.39,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(694.4,643.2)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不是超能力者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就无法和黒子以及大家成为好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:09.99,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(787,639)}<LEVEL 5>                               <Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黒子仰慕的并不是超能力者——常盘台的超电磁砲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是有些小鲁莽而且兴趣低龄向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为学妹著想待人温柔的御坂美琴姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黒子  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别趁机来熊抱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  别说我的兴趣低龄向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…在施以惩戒时毫不留情的这一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是黒子最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Study Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  这家公司的董事当中有一个叫有富春树的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家公司是做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.74,small,NTP,0,0,0,,来  菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.70,small,NTP,0,0,0,,呱太在哪只手里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.45,small,NTP,0,0,0,,这只
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:53.99,small,NTP,0,0,0,,猜对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制药以及各种广域科研
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那所谓的可疑设施是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Study Corporation在第十七学区拥有的工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人在意的是  虽然是不起眼的旧工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却以高价将其买下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工厂的话…是不是制造菲布莉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定那个糖也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.81,small,NTP,0,0,0,,哪只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.56,small,NTP,0,0,0,,这只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要是能知道成份的数据的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来直接潜入调查是最简单快捷的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说时间也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓紧考虑如何改善菲布莉的体质
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是需要那个糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也要获得配方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不容有失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这关乎到菲布莉的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那座桥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想是不会失去任何事物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都笑著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…为了让其实现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细一想  那番话还真是随意得牵强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没想过万一没实现又该怎么办吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有坚信会实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一实验室出现入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵者  是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防御系统已经由SHIFT-A进入了警戒模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为第一实验室并没有好好设置情报防御
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是所谓的诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有人查上门来也没什么大惊小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当下就算查到了第一实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会对我们的计划造成影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么见不得光的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮的数据全都已经转移了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的也只有那个中和剂的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去第一实验室?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会和入侵者一起被驱除的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没打算以身犯险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今计划近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了确保不出万一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去确认下安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是一个人都没有  靠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和上次一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超像是假情报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去后真的能得到报酬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她们会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是知道我会来  特意埋伏在此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子也不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道和菲布莉的制造者是敌对关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗部内部的斗争之类的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  滝壶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.66,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(752,645)}<AIM  Stalker>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有滝壶的「能力追踪」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能追踪曾一度记录到的能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来  玩偷袭是行不通的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:31.17,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(900.8,643.2)}<Powered Suit>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道有人用念力在操纵无人驾驶的驱动铠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是附近没有人的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远程操作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可就算是远程也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.55,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(654.4,644.8)}<Powered Suit>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉在駆动铠里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和构成菲布莉身体物质的成份是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那根头发是作为能力的接收器的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  如此庞大数量凭一人操控的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.86,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(603,648)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该是超能力者级别的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  那根头发的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壶  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像是游泳游太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  气死人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  滝壶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壶  还有谁在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的工作已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  流了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壶  你还是别游了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群家伙还真是暴力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子  可能什么都没留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里面有电源运作的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你稍有动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和你有关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是他们的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你把我的名字告诉菲布莉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中和剂的数据在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中和剂?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那些糖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为觉得对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是我把你的名字告诉菲布莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想到只有你值得依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我想得过于天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天在这个第一实验室发生的骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及在这遇见你  实属幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下菲布莉就有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要将她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个配方是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们救不了菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来加个保险是正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放走了菲布莉的果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅知道了叛徒是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还遇见了大名人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得没错  今天真走运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:41.48,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,640)}<Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次面对面吧  超电磁砲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你那采集到的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了我们不少忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是有富春树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特意到访是为了拯救我们的作品——菲布莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作品?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉果然是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好不要使用电击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道想将真的配方也一起毁掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.43,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,641.6)}<Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个给超电磁砲注射了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不让她动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死不了人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  如果你老实听从命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个给你也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它对我们已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了救菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.14,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(621,646)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来连超能力者也无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经遵从你的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  对哈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉只不过是备用品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,备用品?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们伟大的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮的备用品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和你有关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To tell the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这真的就太长了
